{"tid":314324,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"乞一句道別嘅說話","createTime":"2017-07-09T05:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T19:46:08.000Z","uid":100382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92c7fe7ae133c72bd547de3fd378dfeea8ca6ebb","tid":314324,"uid":100382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:57:29.000Z","msg":"自己衰 抑鬱睇完醫生又唔食藥<br />\n脾氣差到男朋友頂唔順要分手<br />\n醫病嘅動力都係佢<br />\n人又廢 返緊35蚊個鐘嘅工 一日人工420<br />\n都係想儲錢同佢去旅行去玩<br />\n屋企讀書都大壓力 又矮又柒<br />\n真係挨唔住 啲fd都開解過我好多次唔想再煩佢地<br />\n求巴絲們一句道別說話<br />\n要屌求下大家屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1362a14022b9dabede1a775b25c10a799d07e9e","tid":314324,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:03:09.000Z","msg":"Woo 不想你別去<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EfbfpfJzvYg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEfbfpfJzvYg&d=3%2Ffu82qcZ4jJTgeXT1c27JZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7ee7ef1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EfbfpfJzvYg</a>"},{"pid":"f6245d29bf2b7cde5934ce7f17499dd0c001b120","tid":314324,"uid":89166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:04:45.000Z","msg":"落花有意隨流水<br />\n流水無心戀落花"},{"pid":"ca974ce30a4bd3ee93b0d0bf926ad91202b03d7d","tid":314324,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:08:57.000Z","msg":"等我"},{"pid":"e99aa63fc3f8c2d6ffee9fc1c9bb895e5ed049cb","tid":314324,"uid":66355,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:11:39.000Z","msg":"留個tg傾下計好冇呀 唔好做傻事呀"},{"pid":"8374d492d6363fd158aef2eb1529696342cd3e79","tid":314324,"uid":89166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留個tg傾下計好冇呀 唔好做傻事呀</blockquote><br />\n佢句道別係同男朋友講喎好似<br />\n<br />\n做咩傻事"},{"pid":"c3e57faaedaffdb73d7dfa490124bae81db59e60","tid":314324,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:22:28.000Z","msg":"分啦 2017年特殊人